@ risk management

  • Systematic risk
  • Strategic risk
  • Reputation risk
  • Credit risk
  • (Capital-) Market risk: Movements in equity and/or credit on the balance sheet.
  • Liquidity risk: meeting the obligations
  • Operational risk
  • Interest risk: losses because of movements in interest rates
  • Currency risk: losses because of changing exchange rates.

